    "body": "Latest discussion points from @wemeetagain :\n\nUse case would be similar to setting a blank graffiti, ie if you're paranoid about getting identified, attacked w lodestar-specific attacks.\n1. attacker learns about lodestar DoS\n2. attacker scans thru the network, connecting and running identify on all\n3. attacker builds list of lodestar nodes\n4. attacker executes attack on all lodestar nodes\nIssue is a bit misworded since the user agent is part of the identify protocol, not part of gossipsub\nImo still useful but low priority",
